These are Puzzles for 3x4 Level 1

.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-1-1::.
4 different games are played: go, monopoly, canasta, backgammon
The people's birthday is in 4 different months: june, february, july, january
The people use 4 different means of transport: bike, snowmobile, subway, van
1. the person driving the van is on the right of the person driving the snowmobile##1
2. the person playing canasta is on the left of the person playing go##1
3. the person playing backgammon is on the left of the person who's birthday is in july##1
4. the person playing go is the person who's birthday is in june##1
5. the person who's birthday is in june is on the right of the person who's birthday is in july##1
6. the person driving the bike is on the left of the person who's birthday is in january##1
7. the person who's birthday is in february is on the left of the person driving the subway##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |   1    |   2    |     3      |     4      |
| Game    | monopoly  | backgammon | canasta    | go       |
| Birthday         | february | january    | july      | june |
| Transport   | bike   | subway | snowmobile | van        |

