.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-1-2::.
There 4 different types of food: asparagus, broccoli, corn, pear
The people have 4 different hobbies: baking, hiking, rock-climbing, camping
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: western, spy, thriller, romance
1. the person watching romance movies is on the left of the person who's hobby is camping##1
2. the person eating pear is on the right of the person watching thriller movies##1
3. the person who's hobby is rock-climbing is on the right of the person eating corn##1
4. the person watching spy movies is on the left of the person watching romance movies##1
5. the person watching western movies is the person who's hobby is baking##1
6. the person watching romance movies is the person eating broccoli##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |   1    |    2     |       3       |     4     |
| Food        | corn   | broccoli | asparagus     | pear      |
| Hobby         | hiking | rock-climbing | camping | baking |
| Movie-Genre   | spy    | romance   | thriller     | western      |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-1-3::.
The people have 4 different hobbies: gardening, rock-climbing, singing, video-games
There are 4 different favourite colors: mauve, lavender, blue, fuchsia
The people have 4 different jobs:  nurse, dressmaker, bartender, manager
1. the person who likes lavender is on the right of the person who's hobby is gardening##1
2. the dressmaker is on the right of the person who's hobby is singing##1
3. the person who likes fuchsia is on the far left##1
4. the person who's hobby is video-games is the person who likes blue##1
5. the manager is on the right of the person who likes lavender##1
6. the manager is on the right of the bartender##1
7. the person who's hobby is gardening is the nurse##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |       2       |    3    |      4      |
| Hobby         | gardening | rock-climbing | singing | video-games |
| Color   | fuchsia       | lavender    | mauve | blue     |
| Job   | nurse | bartender    | manager | dressmaker    |

