.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-1-4::.
4 different brands of cigars are smoked: ritmeester, bluemaster, chaman, fonseca
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: rowing, rugby, soccer, volleyball
The people's birthday is in 4 different months: october, august, april, june
1. the chaman-smoker is the person who's birthday is in june##1
2. the person who's sport is rugby is on the far left##1
3. the person who's birthday is in april is on the right of the person who's birthday is in june##1
4. the bluemaster-smoker is on the far right##1
5. the person who's sport is soccer is on the far right##1
6. the person who's sport is rowing is the chaman-smoker##1
7. the chaman-smoker is on the left of the person who's sport is soccer##1
8. the fonseca-smoker is on the right of the person who's birthday is in august##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |     1     |        2        |     3      |      4      |
| Cigar         | ritmeester | fonseca | chaman | bluemaster |
| Sport       | rugby     | volleyball      | rowing     | soccer      |
| Birthday   | august | october         | june      | april        |

