.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-1-5::.
The people have 4 different hobbies: cooking, drawing, singing, video-games
The people use 4 different means of transport: boat, train, tram, bus
4 different pets are kept: hedgehog, frog, rat, cat
1. the person driving the train is on the far right##1
2. the person who's hobby is singing is on the far left##1
3. the owner of the frog is on the right of the person driving the boat##1
4. the owner of the hedgehog is the person driving the tram##1
5. the person who's hobby is cooking is on the right of the owner of the frog##1
6. the person who's hobby is cooking is the person driving the train##1
7. the person who's hobby is video-games is the owner of the rat##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |      2      |    3     |      4       |
| Hobby         | singing   | video-games | drawing  | cooking      |
| Transport   | tram  | boat        | bus  | train       |
| Pet         | hedgehog | rat    | frog | cat |

