.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-1-6::.
The people have 4 different jobs:  accountant, designer, mechanic, writer
There 4 different types of food: pumpkin, peach, kale, peas
The people grow 4 different varities of flowers: lily, amaryllis, tulip, rose
1. the accountant is the person who growsamaryllis##1
2. the person who growslily is on the right of the person who growsrose##1
3. the person eating pumpkin is on the right of the writer##1
4. the person who growsrose is on the far left##1
5. the designer is on the far left##1
6. the person eating kale is the mechanic##1
7. the person who growsamaryllis is on the right of the person eating peach##1
8. the writer is the person who growstulip##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |    2     |   3    |     4      |
| Job           | designer | mechanic | writer | accountant |
| Food   | peas   | kale  | peach | pumpkin   |
| Flower   | rose   | lily     | tulip | amaryllis       |

