.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-1-7::.
The people grow 4 different varities of flowers: lily, dahlia, amaryllis, tulip
The people have 4 different hobbies: baking, cooking, skydiving, video-games
4 different games are played: chess, billiard, go, scrabble
1. the person who's hobby is skydiving is on the far right##1
2. the person who growsdahlia is on the far right##1
3. the person playing chess is on the left of the person playing billiard##1
4. the person playing billiard is the person who growsamaryllis##1
5. the person who's hobby is cooking is on the right of the person who growslily##1
6. the person playing go is on the left of the person playing chess##1
7. the person who's hobby is baking is on the right of the person who's hobby is cooking##1
8. the person who's hobby is cooking is the person playing chess##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |     2     |    3    |     4     |
| Flower          | lily  | tulip | amaryllis   | dahlia     |
| Hobby         | video-games | cooking   | baking  | skydiving |
| Game   | go         | chess  | billiard | scrabble  |

