.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-1-8::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: almond-milk, iced-tea, juice, soy-milk
City: paris, boston, nizza, hamburg
There 4 different types of food: tomato, avocado, potato, kiwi
1. the person drinking iced-tea is the person eating potato##1
2. the person eating kiwi is on the right of the person traveling to hamburg##1
3. the person traveling to boston is on the far right##1
4. the person traveling to nizza is on the left of the person eating potato##1
5. the person drinking soy-milk is on the left of the person traveling to paris##1
6. the person eating kiwi is the person drinking juice##1
7. the person eating avocado is on the left of the person eating kiwi##1
8. the person drinking iced-tea is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |     2     |      3      |    4     |
| Beverage      | soy-milk | juice     | almond-milk | iced-tea |
| City   | hamburg  | paris | nizza       | boston    |
| Food   | avocado   | kiwi | tomato    | potato |

