.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-1-9::.
4 different brands of cigars are smoked: game, chaman, bongani, dannemann
4 different games are played: backgammon, chess, billiard, bridge
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: lacrosse, skateboarding, soccer, water-polo
1. the person playing chess is on the right of the dannemann-smoker##1
2. the person who's sport is water-polo is on the right of the person who's sport is soccer##1
3. the person playing chess is on the left of the person playing billiard##1
4. the person who's sport is soccer is the chaman-smoker##1
5. the chaman-smoker is on the right of the person playing bridge##1
6. the person playing bridge is on the right of the bongani-smoker##1
7. the person who's sport is skateboarding is on the left of the person who's sport is lacrosse##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |       1       |    2     |   3    |     4      |
| Cigar          | bongani        | dannemann   | chaman  | game   |
| Game   | backgammon         | bridge     | chess    | billiard       |
| Sport         | skateboarding | lacrosse | soccer | water-polo |

