.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-1-10::.
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: documentary, superhero, time-travel, thriller
4 different games are played: canasta, billiard, chess, bridge
4 different pets are kept: chinchilla, mouse, rabbit, turtle
1. the person watching thriller movies is the owner of the turtle##1
2. the owner of the mouse is on the left of the owner of the rabbit##1
3. the person watching time-travel movies is on the left of the person playing billiard##1
4. the person watching documentary movies is on the right of the owner of the turtle##1
5. the person playing chess is on the far right##1
6. the person watching time-travel movies is on the left of the owner of the turtle##1
7. the person playing canasta is on the right of the person watching superhero movies##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |    1     |    2     |    3    |     4      |
| Movie-Genre   | superhero    | time-travel | thriller | documentary        |
| Game       | bridge | canasta  | billiard | chess     |
| Pet        | mouse    | rabbit   | turtle  | chinchilla |

