.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-1-11::.
The people's birthday is in 4 different months: april, december, july, november
City: colone, prague, boston, rome
The people use 4 different means of transport: airplane, car, scooter, tram
1. the person driving the airplane is on the far left##1
2. the person traveling to colone is on the right of the person who's birthday is in december##1
3. the person traveling to prague is on the left of the person traveling to rome##1
4. the person traveling to colone is on the right of the person traveling to rome##1
5. the person driving the tram is on the right of the person driving the car##1
6. the person driving the airplane is on the left of the person who's birthday is in november##1
7. the person traveling to colone is the person driving the scooter##1
8. the person traveling to boston is the person who's birthday is in april##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |     1      |      2       |       3       |       4       |
| Birthday         | april  | november | december  | july |
| City       | boston | prague        | rome | colone       |
| Transport   | airplane   | car          | tram          | scooter       |

