.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-1-12::.
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: sailing, tennis, surfing, baseball
The people grow 4 different varities of flowers: orchid, begonia, zinnia, azalea
There are 4 different nationalities: canadian, german, pakistani, spanish
1. the person who's sport is sailing is on the right of the person who growsorchid##1
2. the person who growsazalea is the person who's sport is tennis##1
3. the spanish is on the left of the canadian##1
4. the person who growsazalea is on the right of the person who growsbegonia##1
5. the person who's sport is surfing is on the right of the person who's sport is baseball##1
6. the person who's sport is sailing is the pakistani##1
7. the spanish is on the far left##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |     2     |     3      |    4    |
| Sport         | baseball   | surfing   | sailing | tennis |
| Flower   | zinnia | orchid | begonia   | azalea |
| Nationality   | spanish     | canadian  | pakistani  | german  |

