.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-1-13::.
The people have 4 different hobbies: baking, chess, reading, traveling
The people's birthday is in 4 different months: may, october, july, april
City: liverpool, new-york, marseilles, paris
1. the person who's hobby is chess is on the left of the person who's birthday is in april##1
2. the person traveling to marseilles is the person who's birthday is in april##1
3. the person who's hobby is reading is on the right of the person traveling to marseilles##1
4. the person traveling to marseilles is on the left of the person traveling to paris##1
5. the person traveling to liverpool is on the right of the person who's birthday is in october##1
6. the person traveling to marseilles is on the left of the person who's birthday is in may##1
7. the person traveling to liverpool is on the left of the person who's hobby is baking##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |    2     |       3       |    4    |
| Hobby         | traveling | chess    | baking        | reading |
| Birthday   | october     | july     | april        | may   |
| City         | new-york   | liverpool | marseilles | paris  |

