.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-1-14::.
The people have 4 different jobs:  police-officer, chef, analyst, electrician
The people grow 4 different varities of flowers: tulip, iris, azalea, daffodil
The people use 4 different means of transport: car, helicopter, motorbike, roller
1. the police-officer is on the right of the person who growsazalea##1
2. the person driving the helicopter is on the right of the person who growsdaffodil##1
3. the person who growstulip is on the left of the person driving the car##1
4. the person driving the roller is on the left of the person who growsazalea##1
5. the police-officer is on the right of the person driving the helicopter##1
6. the electrician is on the left of the police-officer##1
7. the analyst is on the far right##1
8. the person who growsiris is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |     2      |     3     |     4      |
| Job   | chef   | electrician  | police-officer    | analyst    |
| Flower   | daffodil | azalea  | tulip  | iris |
| Transport     | roller  | helicopter | motorbike | car        |

