.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-1-15::.
There 4 different types of food: lime, grapes, pear, pineapple
There are 4 different nationalities: british, brazilian, nigerian, mexican
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: climbing, handball, soccer, weightlifting
1. the person who's sport is climbing is the person eating pear##1
2. the person eating pear is on the right of the brazilian##1
3. the brazilian is on the right of the mexican##1
4. the person who's sport is handball is on the right of the person who's sport is weightlifting##1
5. the mexican is the person eating pineapple##1
6. the nigerian is on the right of the person who's sport is soccer##1
7. the person eating lime is the british##1
8. the nigerian is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |       1       |    2     |    3     |    4     |
| Food      | lime        | pineapple    | grapes | pear      |
| Nationality   | british        | mexican   | brazilian  | nigerian  |
| Sport         | weightlifting | handball | soccer   | climbing |

