3. the owner of the bird is on the right of the owner of the fish##1
4. the dannemann-smoker is the owner of the horse##1
5. the dunhill-smoker is on the left of the oliveros-smoker##1
6. the person who's sport is biathlon is the oliveros-smoker##1
7. the oliveros-smoker is on the left of the person who's sport is rugby##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |    2     |     3     |     4     |
| Cigar          | ritmeester     | dunhill   | oliveros | dannemann |
| Sport   | surfing | rowing | biathlon | rugby   |
| Pet           | rabbit    | fish     | bird      | horse     |

