.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-1-17::.
The people have 4 different jobs:  architect, bartender, lawyer, scientist
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: water-polo, ice-hockey, climbing, swimming
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: mystery, sports, drama, musical
1. the person who's sport is ice-hockey is on the left of the person watching drama movies##1
2. the bartender is the person who's sport is ice-hockey##1
3. the person who's sport is water-polo is on the right of the person watching sports movies##1
4. the person who's sport is climbing is the person watching sports movies##1
5. the lawyer is on the far left##1
6. the scientist is on the right of the person watching musical movies##1
7. the person watching drama movies is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |     2     |     3      |     4     |
| Job           | lawyer  | architect | bartender  | scientist |
| Sport   | climbing    | water-polo       | ice-hockey | swimming      |
| Movie-Genre   | sports | mystery  | musical    | drama    |

