4. the person who's sport is baseball is on the right of the chef##1
5. the townhouse house is on the far left##1
6. the person who's sport is climbing is on the right of the accountant##1
7. the person who's sport is baseball is on the right of the art-deco house##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |     1      |   2   |    3    |      4      |
