.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-1-20::.
The people's birthday is in 4 different months: november, august, june, october
House: townhouse, art-deco, ranch-style, wooden
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: badminton, biathlon, parkour, tennis
1. the person who's birthday is in august is on the left of the townhouse house##1
2. the person who's sport is badminton is on the left of the person who's birthday is in june##1
3. the person who's sport is tennis is on the far right##1
4. the ranch-style house is on the far right##1
5. the townhouse house is the person who's sport is parkour##1
6. the wooden house is on the far left##1
7. the person who's birthday is in october is on the far right##1
8. the wooden house is on the left of the person who's sport is parkour##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |     2      |     3      |       4        |
| Birthday           | august  | june  | november | october |
| House   | wooden   | townhouse | art-deco   | ranch-style      |
| Sport         | badminton | parkour    | biathlon   | tennis         |

 